anyone to build anything. Our simple to use mobile software uses genetic
algorithms to allow anyone, even children as young as 8, to build real
objects with no experience necessary. Thinker Thing, anyone, anything.

At thinkerthing we propose to make tomorrow's intuitive interfaces of the mind, to literally generate real objects by thought.

We take your big ideas from inception to launch and help you every step of the way of the process.

Think of us as your on-demand build-as-a-service squad that will craft and launch the robust product you need while you gather the internal core team that will make it grow.

Emerging tech has always been our thing and lately we’ve doubled down on blockchain, web3, NFTs, metaverse, dApps, Smart Contracts, DAOs, token-gated rewards and P2E games.

In which capacity would you like us to help you?

1. Product Strategy
Our proprietary Web3 Product Sprint process will turn your concept into execution-ready blueprints. 
Aftwards, you’ll be ready to start building it whether it's with our BaaS Squad or any other shop.

2. Build-as-a-Service on-demand Squads.
You’ll prioritize the features of your product that we’ll estimate, design, develop and release periodically.
The WTD squad will work on your project when each role is required, billing only for that time instead of full/part-time. This keeps incentives mutually aligned, removes friction and is way more flexible.

3. White-labeled NFT solutions: drops + marketplace.
WTD's white label solutions enable you to quickly customize and deliver 100% owned Web3 experiences for a fraction of what it would cost to develop from scratch: Generative NFT drops, NFT marketplace (auctions + fixed price + P2P secondary market), play to earn games  and token-gated rewards.
